hmmmm why is it that every magical girl in hentai series always weak in their mind?

But the worst aspect of the timidness of the first piercing laden girl is that her confidence was crushed. Either this was done via an abuser or it was just a symptom of her mental illness and insecurities. There is nothing actually wrong with her, she's perfectly adequate, but she doesn't ever step on someone else's toes. That's the sign of an abused dog to me. This is a pretty dark story. Fortunately the 'dom' that shows up lasts not even half as long and the majority of her dominance is that she denies the fact that she's inferior and gaslights people.

I noticed that the dialogue is excessive, anyway, onto characterization.

The first 'antagonist' feels a dearth of confidence. The style of domination is also damaging, her breast piercings permanently scar her flesh, something which most people would avoid in reality. A lot of the dominance in this is negative, one of the first things which the apparent 'mistress' uses is awe. Awe to strike fear into people. I suspect more than a few would have told this madame to fuck off.
